room_title: Escape room "Secret Study" by Padlock Escape Games in College Station
review: This is the best escape room in College Station (I have escaped all 7 currently running).  It is fun, surprising, and actually escapable.

room_title: Escape room "Secret Study" by Padlock Escape Games in College Station
review: My friends and I came here for a bachelorette party. We did the Secret Study and had so much fun! I cannot wait to come back to try the other rooms.
